2007-07-31  Jop... (Jonas F. Jensen) <jopsen@gmail.com> 

	* libLastRip/MetaInfo.cs: Implementing ID3v2 support using
	  TagLib-Sharp.
	* libLastRip/LastManager/LastManager.cs: Replacing RemoveIllegalChars()
	  with RemoveInvalidPathChars() and RemoveInvalidFileNameChars(),
	  fixing issue 4
	  (http://code.google.com/p/thelastripper/issues/detail?id=4). New
	  solution only removes chars defined by invalid by the framework
	  (System.IO.Path.GetInvalidFileNameChars() and
	  System.IO.Path.GetInvalidPathChars()).
	* taglib-sharp/taglib-sharp.dll: Adding taglib-sharp as binary, source
	  is only release through SVN, not included in build process or
	  source releases.

